Paper: 14115980
Title: Comment on "Localization of 5D Elko Spinors on Minkowski Branes"
Authors: I. C. Jardim and G. Alencar and R. R. Landim and R. N. Costa Filho
Abstract: We show that the statement in Yu-Xiao Liu, Xiang-Nan Zhou, Ke Yang and Feng-Wei Chen [Phys. Rev. D 86 , 064012 (2012)] that the zero mode of ELKO spinor is localized in some thin brane scenarios is not correct. This reopens the problem of localization of ELKO spinors.
